WEBVTT

00:15.760 --> 00:17.468
♪

00:20.384 --> 00:21.384
Who are you?

00:21.468 --> 00:23.384
I'm the one who strung
your chief of police up.

00:24.343 --> 00:27.051
Can I have my pills, please?
Helps me get my memory.

00:28.259 --> 00:29.760
Long time since I've been home.

00:30.676 --> 00:33.092
Welcome to your family tree.

00:33.760 --> 00:35.593
These are
your great grandparents,

00:35.760 --> 00:38.801
tragically killed
in the massacre of 1921.

00:45.926 --> 00:48.676
If you want her to know
who you are, just tell her.

00:48.760 --> 00:50.051
She's not gonna listen.

00:50.967 --> 00:52.009
What are these?

00:52.092 --> 00:53.676
I was hoping you could ask
your ex.

00:54.343 --> 00:55.426
It's Nostalgia.

00:55.801 --> 00:57.051
They outlawed those.

00:57.134 --> 00:59.301
So I highly recommend
you tell your lady-friend

00:59.384 --> 01:00.384
not to take them.

01:01.051 --> 01:02.134
These are memories.

01:02.384 --> 01:03.468
Whose memories?

01:03.885 --> 01:05.384
They're my grandfather's.

01:05.843 --> 01:07.092
Show me your hands!

01:07.343 --> 01:08.384
Cuff her. Now.

01:08.468 --> 01:10.384
- What did you fucking do?!
- I had to.

01:10.468 --> 01:11.801
♪

01:12.967 --> 01:14.343
