01:28.009 --> 01:30.176
Man:
Hooded Justice.

01:30.801 --> 01:32.676
It all started with you.

01:32.760 --> 01:34.343
You're the alpha, pal.

01:34.426 --> 01:36.468
It was your idea
to put on that mask

01:36.551 --> 01:38.593
and fight crime.

01:38.676 --> 01:40.760
As fellow enforcers of
the law, I gotta tell you

01:40.843 --> 01:44.468
what an honor it is to sit
across from you right now.

01:45.676 --> 01:47.343
Captain Axis,

01:47.426 --> 01:49.301
King Mob, Moloch...

01:49.384 --> 01:52.301
The worst villains in the city,
all in jail thanks to you

01:52.384 --> 01:56.009
and your buddies, the Minutemen.

01:56.092 --> 01:58.259
You're true American heroes,
all of yous.

01:58.343 --> 02:02.134
But you, Hooded Justice,
you most of all

02:02.217 --> 02:06.384
because, like I said,
you were the first.

02:07.718 --> 02:09.426
Hey, help us settle a bet.

02:09.509 --> 02:12.384
What's the story with
that noose around your neck?

02:12.468 --> 02:15.092
See, I-I think it's
an executioner thing.

02:15.176 --> 02:18.301
You know, let your enemies
know you mean business.

02:18.384 --> 02:20.843
But, Jerry here...
Jerry, how about you tell him

02:20.926 --> 02:23.343
what you think
that noose is for?

02:23.426 --> 02:25.134
Sex stuff.

02:25.217 --> 02:28.635
-What do you want from me?
-Agent: We want you to take
that fucking hood off

02:28.718 --> 02:32.051
so we can take a photo
of your beautiful face.

02:32.134 --> 02:34.092
Never.

02:34.176 --> 02:37.676
Look, pal, we don't
know who you are,

02:37.760 --> 02:39.551
but we know what you do,

02:39.635 --> 02:42.885
and... who you do.

02:45.134 --> 02:47.426
Captain Metropolis,

02:47.509 --> 02:49.301
aka Nelson Gardner,

02:49.384 --> 02:52.426
aka your fairy princess.

02:52.509 --> 02:54.384
He's got a safe
behind the painting

02:54.468 --> 02:56.301
of the white horse
in his boudoir.

02:56.384 --> 02:59.009
Now, in that safe
is a roll of film.

02:59.092 --> 03:01.426
Jerry, you wanna tell
him what's on that film?

03:02.217 --> 03:04.092
Sex stuff.

03:04.926 --> 03:06.259
Agent:
That's right.

03:06.343 --> 03:10.509
Your boyfriend has got
other boyfriends,

03:10.593 --> 03:13.217
and he's trying to blackmail
Director Hoover

03:13.301 --> 03:15.843
just because he bears
a passing resemblance

03:15.926 --> 03:18.009
to the fellow
Captain Bigcockalus

03:18.092 --> 03:20.259
is violating on that film.

03:20.343 --> 03:23.676
A fellow who is
not Director Hoover

03:23.760 --> 03:27.426
because Director Hoover is
not a depraved homosexual.

03:27.509 --> 03:30.176
So, you're gonna bring
us that film,

03:30.259 --> 03:33.468
and we're gonna rip up the photo
we're about to take of you.

03:33.885 --> 03:35.509
Why should I trust you?

03:35.593 --> 03:38.635
Because Jerry and me,
we won't show it to anybody.

03:38.718 --> 03:41.843
Hell, nobody even knows
we're here with you right now.

03:41.926 --> 03:43.468
This is all hush-hush.

03:44.176 --> 03:46.926
Just the way you
like it, sweetheart.

03:48.009 --> 03:49.468
So...

03:50.926 --> 03:53.134
what do you say, HJ?

04:07.718 --> 04:09.301
Agent:
Well, well.

04:10.301 --> 04:12.967
Ain't you pretty.

04:14.551 --> 04:16.384
Jerry...

04:16.468 --> 04:18.635
