04:23.843 --> 04:25.843
Say cheese.

04:30.343 --> 04:31.509
Aah!

05:10.885 --> 05:12.343
Cheese.

05:14.926 --> 05:16.402
Hooded Justice:
I should probably be worried

05:16.426 --> 05:18.509
that I just murdered
two federal agents,

05:18.593 --> 05:21.259
but all I could think about
is that Nelson Gardner

05:21.343 --> 05:24.301
is cheating on me,
with J. Edgar Hoover no less...

05:24.384 --> 05:26.593
Turn that shit off.

