when you can live in the past?

06:24.551 --> 06:25.885
Well, you know the rest.

06:25.967 --> 06:28.801
People got hooked,
dependency, ODs.

06:28.885 --> 06:31.092
So, Redford and the FDA
outlawed it,

06:31.176 --> 06:33.801
and the company
that made it had to stop.

06:33.885 --> 06:36.468
And do you know
who owns that company?

06:37.801 --> 06:39.009
Lady Trieu.

06:39.092 --> 06:40.384
Coincidence.

06:40.468 --> 06:42.801
Hey, maybe she knows
your Grandpa.

06:42.885 --> 06:44.384
Grandpa.

06:44.468 --> 06:46.259
Those were his pills
you swallowed, Angela.

06:46.343 --> 06:49.885
That's very, very bad...

06:49.967 --> 06:53.718
You're not supposed to take
someone else's Nostalgia.

06:54.343 --> 06:56.819
You need to sign this release
so we can get your
stomach pumped.

06:56.843 --> 06:58.760
