07:24.551 --> 07:26.676
Is it starting?

07:27.843 --> 07:31.092
God damn it.
Do you know where
your grandfather is, Angela?

07:31.176 --> 07:33.051
Blake: Where is he?

07:33.134 --> 07:35.551
Where is your grandfather?!

07:36.843 --> 07:38.384
Where?

07:38.468 --> 07:40.134
Where is he?

07:55.217 --> 07:59.551
I want you to think
about what you're wearing,

08:00.967 --> 08:03.217
