when you wake up,

08:04.176 --> 08:06.384
what you take off
when you go to bed.

08:08.843 --> 08:12.551
The uniform a man wears
changes him.

08:15.259 --> 08:18.551
Make sure yours changes
you for the better.

08:21.551 --> 08:24.259
And God bless you
for taking an oath...

08:25.926 --> 08:28.051
