Do us proud.
Be safe out there.

09:11.301 --> 09:15.259
Looks like I get the honor
of putting a badge on you.

09:16.384 --> 09:18.718
- What's your name, Officer?
- William Reeves, sir,

09:18.801 --> 09:20.509
and the honor is mine,
Lieutenant Battle.

09:20.593 --> 09:22.551
I joined the force
because of you.

09:22.635 --> 09:24.801
Sorry to hear that.

09:24.885 --> 09:27.176
