09:54.635 --> 09:56.967
Here you go, June.

09:57.051 --> 10:00.384
Thank you, Officer.

10:00.468 --> 10:03.426
Thanks for coming today.
Meant a lot to see
a friendly face.

10:03.509 --> 10:05.760
I was there for work, not you.

10:05.843 --> 10:07.885
So, why are you writing
your story about me?

10:07.967 --> 10:10.301
Because the Amsterdam
says a Negro cadet

10:10.384 --> 10:12.676
making the force is big news.

10:12.760 --> 10:14.926
So, I'm big news.

10:15.009 --> 10:16.760
You're a big something,

10:16.843 --> 10:19.760
but it ain't news, Officer.

10:19.843 --> 10:22.736
-You gonna keep calling me that?
-If you don't want me
to call you officer,

10:22.760 --> 10:25.259
you probably should've chosen
a different line of work.

10:25.343 --> 10:27.676
All right.
Let me have it.

10:28.384 --> 10:31.176
- Let you have what?
- I know what you're thinking.

10:33.426 --> 10:35.426
June:
What am I thinking?

10:35.509 --> 10:37.301
Will:
I've joined the enemy.

10:37.384 --> 10:39.384
The police in this city

10:39.468 --> 10:41.009
smother our people
under their shoes.

10:41.092 --> 10:44.134
Lieutenant Battle is a Tom,
and now I am a Tom too.

10:44.217 --> 10:46.134
They just hired me
for the publicity.

10:46.217 --> 10:49.801
And besides all of that,
you're worried about me.

10:49.885 --> 10:52.635
They gave you a gun and a stick.

10:52.718 --> 10:54.635
That's what I'm worried about.

10:54.718 --> 10:57.217
What you're gonna do with them.

10:57.301 --> 10:59.967
Because you are an angry,

11:00.051 --> 11:02.718
angry man, William Reeves.

11:04.551 --> 11:05.967
I'm not angry.

11:11.885 --> 11:15.051
It's okay.
Most of us are.

11:15.967 --> 11:19.217
I'm young, I'm healthy,
I got the job I always wanted.

11:19.301 --> 11:21.176
What have I got
to be angry about?

11:21.259 --> 11:24.551
Folks were murdered
right in front of you.

11:24.635 --> 11:26.760
Right in front of you.

11:26.843 --> 11:29.426
The whole town, all of them.

11:29.509 --> 11:31.092
Your mother and your father...

11:31.176 --> 11:32.801
That was a long time ago.

11:34.593 --> 11:36.760
I don't wanna live in the past.

11:37.926 --> 11:40.384
And that, Will Reeves,

11:40.468 --> 11:43.718
is why you are
so goddamned angry.

12:12.635 --> 12:14.801
Officer. Good evening.

12:14.885 --> 12:16.468
Evening.

12:43.885 --> 12:46.092
