12:57.885 --> 12:59.468
Stop in the name of the law!

12:59.551 --> 13:03.343
Ha! I thought they only
said that in the pictures.

13:04.217 --> 13:06.259
- So, what is it?
- Huh?

13:06.343 --> 13:08.509
The name of the law.

13:10.051 --> 13:11.676
Who are you, boy?

13:14.468 --> 13:16.843
What's your name?

13:17.885 --> 13:19.343
Fred.

13:20.092 --> 13:21.967
Now, if you'll excuse me,

13:22.051 --> 13:24.217
I wanna get home
in time for Amos 'n' Andy.

13:24.301 --> 13:26.051
I saw what you did.

13:26.134 --> 13:28.760
Oh, you mean at that fine

13:28.843 --> 13:31.343
Jewish delicatessen over there?

13:31.426 --> 13:34.676
You know, I heard
they have a rat problem.

13:35.301 --> 13:38.718
Maybe one chewed through
the wires, started a fire.

13:38.801 --> 13:41.009
You're under arrest.

13:41.092 --> 13:42.801
Oh...

13:42.885 --> 13:44.843
I seriously doubt that.

13:49.551 --> 13:52.259
I'm booking this man for arson.
He burned down a delicatessen

13:52.343 --> 13:55.259
- on Jamaica Avenue.
- That is not what happened, sir.

13:55.343 --> 13:57.843
I was just out for
an evening constitutional.

13:57.926 --> 13:59.885
Officer:
Mm-hmm.

13:59.967 --> 14:02.176
Must be a case
of mistaken identity.

14:02.259 --> 14:04.509
That's a lie. I saw him
do it with my own eyes!

14:04.593 --> 14:07.051
- Everything okay?
- Will: Yes, it's fine.

14:07.134 --> 14:08.801
Fellas, this spook

14:08.885 --> 14:12.092
is accusing me of
a horrendous crime.

14:12.926 --> 14:16.468
Who you gonna believe,
me or him?

14:16.926 --> 14:20.134
What'd you just call
our fellow officer?

14:20.635 --> 14:22.009
Nothing.

14:22.092 --> 14:25.259
-Sorry, I...
-Don't apologize to me.
You apologize to him.

14:30.718 --> 14:32.009
I'm so sorry.

14:32.092 --> 14:35.134
- We'll book this fink.
- But Reeves made the arrest.

14:35.217 --> 14:37.176
- We got it from here.
- Yeah.

14:37.259 --> 14:40.384
- Sure, okay.
- Good work, Officer Reeves.

14:40.468 --> 14:43.593
