15:04.468 --> 15:06.885
- Beats the news, huh?
- Yeah.

15:06.967 --> 15:08.635
More hopeful.

15:08.718 --> 15:11.551
- What's it about?
- A boy, a baby,

15:11.635 --> 15:13.885
his-his father put
him in a rocket ship

15:13.967 --> 15:15.843
and sent him
to Earth just before

15:15.926 --> 15:17.509
his planet explodes.

15:17.593 --> 15:20.217
- Young Will:
Will you come, too?

15:20.301 --> 15:22.801
Will's Mother:
We're gonna be
right behind you.

15:24.967 --> 15:26.509
Hey!

15:30.009 --> 15:32.176
Pardon me, Officer.

15:46.301 --> 15:47.760
- You let him go?
- Let who go?

15:47.843 --> 15:50.967
The man I brought in for
burning down a deli. Fred.

15:51.051 --> 15:54.551
Sorry. I got no idea
what you're talking about.

15:54.635 --> 15:56.635
What? You were
standing right there!

15:56.718 --> 15:58.926
The other officers took
the guy to book him.

15:59.009 --> 16:01.551
I think you're having
memory problems, Reeves.

16:01.635 --> 16:03.926
My memory is fine.

16:04.009 --> 16:06.885
Just let it be, okay?

16:08.092 --> 16:10.134
I saw them do this to you.

16:10.217 --> 16:11.926
What does this mean?
What is it?

16:12.009 --> 16:15.760
It's gonna be
the hole in your head
if you don't let it be.

16:15.843 --> 16:18.009
I'm trying to help
you out here, Reeves.

16:18.092 --> 16:20.217
Go home, please.

16:30.092 --> 16:33.217
