33:42.092 --> 33:43.509
Have you heard of him?

33:43.593 --> 33:46.092
- Costumed adventurer?
- Yes.

33:46.176 --> 33:50.051
Crime fighting in disguise.
It's a new phenomenon,

33:50.134 --> 33:52.009
