by forming a team.

33:57.551 --> 33:59.635
Patriots, heroes.

34:00.343 --> 34:03.593
They call themselves
the New Minutemen.

34:04.176 --> 34:06.301
It's a great group of fellows,

34:06.384 --> 34:09.551
and there's even
a couple of ladies.

34:13.509 --> 34:15.051
I'm sorry,
but I don't understand

34:15.134 --> 34:17.259
what this has got to do with me.

34:17.718 --> 34:21.301
The team is incomplete without
the hero who inspired them.

34:21.885 --> 34:24.009
Hooded Justice.

34:25.718 --> 34:28.801
Captain Metropolis is
a master of strategy.

34:28.885 --> 34:30.676
He scrutinized
the different locations

34:30.760 --> 34:32.092
where Hooded Justice appeared,

34:32.176 --> 34:34.843
and cross-referenced them
with patrols of local police.

34:35.468 --> 34:37.635
- So, you think he's a cop?
