34:38.509 --> 34:41.134
I believe a cop is
feeding him intelligence

34:41.217 --> 34:43.801
about criminal activity.

34:44.509 --> 34:47.426
But you know all
about this, Officer Reeves,

34:47.509 --> 34:49.301
because that cop is you.

34:52.718 --> 34:54.217
I'm sorry?

34:54.301 --> 34:56.635
I didn't mean that as a joke.

34:56.718 --> 35:00.301
Mind if I ask, is this
strategic mastermind,

35:00.384 --> 35:02.843
Captain Metropolis, blond?

35:03.593 --> 35:05.718
About your height?

35:06.676 --> 35:08.092
I...

35:08.176 --> 35:09.652
I don't understand
what you're implying...

35:09.676 --> 35:13.217
- What does the word
"cyclops" mean to you?
- Not much.

35:14.426 --> 35:16.843
Is it some kind of underground
criminal enterprise

35:16.926 --> 35:18.760
that Hooded Justice
is investigating?

35:18.843 --> 35:20.509
Well, if you consider
the Ku Klux Klan

35:20.593 --> 35:22.843
a criminal enterprise, then yes.

35:23.426 --> 35:25.343
And they're planning something.

35:25.426 --> 35:28.676
Sounds like a job for
the Minutemen all right.

35:30.635 --> 35:33.134
Let's say I do know
Hooded Justice.

35:33.217 --> 35:36.009
- Why should he join your team?
- He shouldn't.

35:39.635 --> 35:43.009
He should join
because brave men like him

35:43.092 --> 35:45.217
are rare specimens.

35:45.967 --> 35:48.384
Why fight alone,

35:48.468 --> 35:51.718
when you could have
true companionship?

35:55.051 --> 35:56.426
Well,

35:56.509 --> 35:59.384
I have overstayed my welcome.

36:00.926 --> 36:03.718
But I hope you do know
Hooded Justice, Officer Reeves.

36:04.676 --> 36:07.468
If only to tell him
what a huge admirer

36:07.551 --> 36:09.718
Captain Metropolis is.

36:10.217 --> 36:13.009
Something tells me
they have a lot in common.

36:17.967 --> 36:21.343
Good evening, Mrs. Reeves.
Again, I am...

36:21.426 --> 36:23.593
so sorry to have intruded.

36:25.217 --> 36:27.384
I'll see myself out.

36:33.760 --> 36:34.760
No.

36:34.843 --> 36:37.843
Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!

36:37.926 --> 36:40.259
Oh, yes!

