37:01.468 --> 37:03.301
What?

37:03.384 --> 37:04.926
That I was...

37:05.009 --> 37:06.967
Hooded Justice.

37:07.926 --> 37:09.801
The moment I laid eyes on you.

37:09.885 --> 37:12.635
You're lying. You thought
he was a white man.

37:13.426 --> 37:15.009
True.

37:15.885 --> 37:17.843
