45:15.301 --> 45:17.760
- Can you tell me
what happened here?
- I don't...

45:17.843 --> 45:21.426
- I-I don't know.
- I can't...

45:22.551 --> 45:25.134
When the picture started...

45:26.509 --> 45:28.967
there was a-a flicker...

45:30.217 --> 45:32.926
a bright light
going on and off...

