to... hurt people,

45:44.468 --> 45:46.593
and I think...

45:46.676 --> 45:48.676
I think maybe I did that.

45:51.259 --> 45:54.259
I heard a voice
inside my head and...

46:03.343 --> 46:05.092
Beware of the Cyclops.

