people should know.

46:38.967 --> 46:42.593
The residents of Harlem
cause riots all on their own.

46:42.676 --> 46:44.885
No, no! This is real!

46:45.760 --> 46:48.426
It's some kind of mesmerism.

46:49.843 --> 46:52.384
That book I found...

46:52.468 --> 46:55.885
- Cyclops is...
