Cyclops, Cyclops.

46:55.967 --> 46:58.343
Dear God. So, the Klan

46:58.426 --> 47:01.051
is using mind control?

47:01.134 --> 47:04.967
Do you have any idea how
ridiculous that sounds?

47:05.051 --> 47:06.718
Have you been drinking?

47:06.801 --> 47:10.384
- No.
- Well, maybe you should be.

47:10.468 --> 47:13.635
Come over. You can bring
